713
00:41:22.967 --> 00:41:26.736
♪ No one knows what it's like ♪
The only question is...

714
00:41:26.738 --> 00:41:29.105
♪ To be the bad man ♪
...Will you help me?

715
00:41:29.107 --> 00:41:34.176
♪ To be the sad man ♪

716
00:41:34.178 --> 00:41:35.807
